	* config.sub: 2021-01-08 (repaired)
	    From: Peixing Xin <peixing.xin@windriver.com>
	    config.sub: recognize four-part configuration name for VxWorks

	    For example:

	      armv7m-wrs-vxworks-eabihf
	      armv7-wrs-vxworks-eabihf
