	* AcSplit/CF_RESTARTABLE_PIPEREAD: fix typo in comment

2020-01-16  Thomas E. Dickey  <dickey@invisible-island.net>

	* AcSplit/CF_X_ATHENA_CPPFLAGS:
	fix the last change - CPPFLAGS was not updated properly

