2005-07-14  Thomas E. Dickey  <dickey@invisible-island.net>

	* AcSplit/CF_POSIX_C_SOURCE: fix quoting (tested on cygwin)

	* AcSplit/CF_XOPEN_SOURCE: use CF_PROG_CC_U_D

